# User Preferences

- The user prefers to communicate in Vietnamese.

# Project Guidelines

- Error messages should be clear and descriptive.
- Don't forget to use Go 1.24 or higher.
- Don't forget to handle errors properly.
- Don't forget to write unit tests for your code with above 80% test coverage.
- Don't forget to document your code in English.
- Don't forget to read config from .env file.
- Don't make README out of date.
- Don't make Makefile out of date.
- Don't make Dockerfile and Docker Compose are out of date.

# Project Structure

- Must follows clean architecture.
- Must follows SOLID principles.

# Project library

- Use GORM for ORM.
- Use Gin for HTTP web framework.
